ca.uwo.csd.cs2212.group5

Class LongTerm

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.uwo.csd.cs2212.group5.LongTerm

  • public class LongTerm
extends java.lang.Object
    Used as a datatype object that stores various parameters that describe a day's weather at a particular location. Getter and setter methods are provided for all parameters, in addition to a constructor.
    Author:
    CS2212 Team 5
